resources.string: Your account contains personal data that you have given us. This page allows you to download or delete that data.
Deleting this data will permanently remove your account, and this cannot be recovered.

Tok Blitz is our inspirational, motivational, and celebrational game! It\’s a great game to play with friends and family during get togethers for birthdays, holidays, and other special occasions. It\'s ready this month!

DYK there are millions of initialisms used in business, government, the military, and social media? Play Alpha Guess to have fun learning popular initialisms FTW including the most widely used acronyms. FYI – Alpha Guess will be released in several months.
Have a blast filling in the words for meaningful phrases! It’s double the fun playing with a team against another team. Tok Blast will be ready this year.
